      <textAnnotation id="sid-FA4A2B73-6E55-468F-9FA6-1B0E0BCE5EE4" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>L3 Description:
Test various pricing scenarios against each supplier's bid and compare to cost target. SAP enables you to compare the different quotes received. But price simulation is only a part of the analysis. The quantitative part should have a weight compare to the qualitative analysis in order to evaluate the best supplier overall.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-3852582B-544E-42DF-8B04-5662BD2C8058" signavio:alignment="left">
